text:
Hi, I'm having trouble finding the information needed to bind the style of the fonts with the designer into a custom template.
main.css: I thought about doing this NB font-familly works, but not font-style (bold, italic):
font-family: {{theme.font.font}};
font-style: {{theme.font.styles}};
Fields.json: I defined do so:
{
        "name" : "font",
        "label" : "Font",
        "required" : false,
        "locked" : false,
        "load_external_fonts" : true,
        "type" : "font",
        "default" : {
          "size" : 12,
          "font":"Times New Roman",
          "font_set":"GOOGLE",
          "size_unit" : "px",
          "color" : "#000",
          "styles" : { 
            
          }
        },
        "visibility" : {
          "hidden_subfields" : {
            "color": true,
            "font": false,
            "size": true
          }
        }
      }

When i click on bold button in designer, nothing append, but if i change the font-family its work !  I can't find how to do it

do you have any way to do it?

Thanks a lot
